# Per-Dockerfile ignore (BuildKit) for Dockerfile.training-service — takes
# precedence over the root .dockerignore. Allowlist: only what the build
# COPYs. Unlike every other context, this one ADMITS training-service/assets/
# — the ~3.5GB SAM3 checkpoint is baked into this image only.
*
!training-service/
!training-service/**
!proto/
!proto/**
training-service/tests
**/__pycache__
*.pyc
